âTis no matter for that, his wit will excuse that.
A wit should no more be sincere than a woman constant: one argues a decay of parts, as tâother of beauty.
MIRA.  Maybe you think him too positive?
WIT.  No, no; his being positive is an incentive to argument, and keeps up conversation.
