He will lie like a chambermaid, or a woman of qualityâs porter.
Now that is a fault.
SCENE VII.                             [_To them_] COACHMAN.  COACH.  Is Master Petulant here, mistress?
BET.  Yes.
COACH.  Three gentlewomen in a coach would speak with him.
FAIN.  O brave Petulant!
